          "title": "Serotonergic combinations",
          "body": "Fluoxetine–tramadol teaching is about escalating serotonin toxicity risk to the clinician, not inventing a switch. Confirm against current SA guidance and the labelled products.",
          "publishState": "published"
        }
      ],
